description:
Proudly presented by the team at Soultani Property Group Blacktown, this stunning & fully renovated two-bedroom unit promises a comfortable and convenient lifestyle as well as a great rental return! The location is sought-after, being walking distance to local Schools, Shops, bus stops, Blacktown Station, T-Way, Blacktown Westpoint, Blacktown Aquatic Centre & many more! For investors, singles, couples or downsizers, this property is sure to tick the boxes.

Features include:
+ 2 large bedrooms, main with built-in robe
+ Open plan living & dining areas
+ Dining area fitted with storage cabinets
+ Modern kitchen with ample bench space
+ Renovated main bathroom with bath & shower & floor to ceiling tiles
+ Private balcony perfect for entertaining
+ Internal laundry
+ Downlights throughout
+ Secure lock-up single garage

For your chance to secure this stunning home, contact Blacktown's number 1 premier agents Hash Soultani on 0451 627 488 or Ashlee Rando on 0450 606 454.
